---
title: Spicy Mussel Laksa in Coconut Curry with Noodles and Snow Peas
description: Laksa is taking centre stage tonight, with mussels as its leading lady. Our version of this hearty curry noodle soup is a take on the Singaporean laksa lemak, which uses coconut milk and lime to draw highlight the Southeast Asian flavours.
